column5: Man this week is going to be tough...I'm off today, tomorrow, and Friday, sadly I have to go to work Saturday    ( man that's going to be one long day   ) then I'm on VACATION!!!!  I'll spend a couple of days getting the house cleaned up, another couple of days making sure my new dog gets to know my mom so she'll let her in the house    then Wed. morning, I'm off to Lakair   for some much needed R&R  Maureen
WOOOOOOOOOOOO HOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOO!!!! LAKAIR!!!!  Can you tell I'm looking forward to it??
